WEBVTT

00:00:15.890 --> 00:00:17.058
That is correct.

00:00:17.726 --> 00:00:20.061
As Balancer of the three worlds
comprised of the Soul Society,

00:00:20.145 --> 00:00:23.648
the World of the Living,
and Hueco Mundo…

00:00:23.732 --> 00:00:27.110
I came to propose
a non-aggression pact

00:00:27.193 --> 00:00:30.405
between the Soul Society
and the Licht Reich.

00:00:31.948 --> 00:00:34.743
Let us Soul Reapers worry
about the world and

00:00:34.826 --> 00:00:38.747
enjoy the prosperity of your empire.

00:00:39.664 --> 00:00:43.585
It goes without saying that
we will not interfere

00:00:43.668 --> 00:00:45.962
with the unification of the Quincies
by the Licht Reich.

00:00:46.588 --> 00:00:48.590
It is a win-win pact.

00:00:48.631 --> 00:00:50.633
I see no reason to refuse.

00:00:52.761 --> 00:00:53.928
It is a deception.

00:00:56.389 --> 00:00:59.267
You take me lightly as if
I am some ignorant baby.

00:00:59.434 --> 00:01:03.480
Ah… That was never my intention.

00:01:03.730 --> 00:01:06.524
But you indeed know nothing.

00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:12.197
Then let me ask you this.
The world was once one.

00:01:12.739 --> 00:01:16.034
Who set boundaries to
that eternal peace

00:01:16.117 --> 00:01:18.953
by separating life and death?

00:01:19.287 --> 00:01:20.789
The Soul King.

00:01:21.289 --> 00:01:24.834
Who brought the fear of death
to the people?

00:01:25.251 --> 00:01:27.504
That would also be the Soul King.

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:33.760
I know the anguished cries of the souls
that have returned to me…

00:01:34.010 --> 00:01:36.805
I know the vindictiveness of the people

00:01:36.971 --> 00:01:40.809
who fear death and cling to
their fleeting lives.

00:01:41.392 --> 00:01:46.022
And that's the answer
you have to offer,

00:01:46.147 --> 00:01:48.441
Ichibe Hyosube?

00:01:49.109 --> 00:01:51.945
Don't say my name so lightly.

00:01:52.612 --> 00:01:56.783
Where, in these three worlds,
can one find peace?

00:01:57.867 --> 00:01:59.452
– I can see it all.
– I'll show it to you.

00:02:18.346 --> 00:02:21.182
So that's…the Soul King?

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:24.894
You see? You knew nothing.

00:02:25.186 --> 00:02:31.234
We, together with the Soul King,
maintain this fragile world.

00:02:32.402 --> 00:02:35.905
How pitiful… How…

00:02:36.865 --> 00:02:38.032
repulsive!

00:02:39.868 --> 00:02:43.204
I told you I can see it all,
Ichibe Hyosube!

00:02:43.955 --> 00:02:46.791
Do you think you can kill me
with that hand?

00:02:46.875 --> 00:02:49.878
My father's hand is nothing more
than a sacrifice to his child.

00:02:49.961 --> 00:02:53.047
It can give life,
but cannot take it away.

00:02:53.381 --> 00:02:56.384
Those eyes of yours
are sure troublesome…

00:02:56.718 --> 00:03:00.930
But they can never see through
the Soul King.

00:03:05.268 --> 00:03:06.561
What…?!

00:03:07.812 --> 00:03:11.608
Did you think I'd let you have
the Soul King's arm for free?

00:03:13.484 --> 00:03:18.698
Your eyes will be closed forever,
never to open until the day you die.

00:03:19.282 --> 00:03:21.326
Live a modest life.

00:03:24.078 --> 00:03:26.873
I'm glad I lost these eyes.

00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:30.084
I no longer have to see through
your humiliation anymore.

00:03:30.752 --> 00:03:33.922
Soul King, my father,
you have become nothing

00:03:34.047 --> 00:03:38.134
but a mindless and hideous lump
of flesh to be worshipped…

00:03:38.927 --> 00:03:41.804
I will give you a new purpose.

00:03:43.389 --> 00:03:46.517
Vanish along with this world.

00:03:46.768 --> 00:03:49.854
Become a grave to the three worlds.

00:03:52.857 --> 00:03:54.484
I see…

00:03:55.276 --> 00:03:57.862
So this is the Royal Palace.

00:03:59.614 --> 00:04:02.242
I feel your pain, Your Majesty.

00:04:02.450 --> 00:04:05.286
What are you talking about, Haschwalth?

00:04:06.621 --> 00:04:12.126
I'm not feeling a shred of emotion
from looking at this decaying grave.

00:04:14.003 --> 00:04:15.630
My apologies.

00:04:16.381 --> 00:04:17.632
Let's go.

00:04:17.924 --> 00:04:20.802
We will end this world full of deceit

00:04:20.843 --> 00:04:25.682
and create a new world of true peace…

00:04:26.808 --> 00:04:28.851
with our own hands.

00:05:00.341 --> 00:05:05.888
Oh, my darling, I don't even know
where my heart has gone

00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:11.811
And I've forgotten
that dream I once had

00:05:12.020 --> 00:05:17.066
Becoming an adult =
keeping a public face and bluffing?

00:05:17.775 --> 00:05:23.948
Tell me, what is reflected
in the painted-over mirror?

00:05:24.615 --> 00:05:29.787
Your photo is starting to fade

00:05:30.330 --> 00:05:34.876
Leaving me, as I change

00:05:35.001 --> 00:05:40.715
I'll shout at the top of my voice
as it pierces through the night

00:05:41.049 --> 00:05:46.554
Burning my chest,
formless fear and all

00:05:46.888 --> 00:05:52.435
It's okay if I can't laugh
like that day

00:05:52.518 --> 00:05:58.274
Sadness, scars, everything…
I want to take them all with me

00:05:59.275 --> 00:06:01.736
You can't kill my vibe, oh baby

00:06:01.736 --> 00:06:04.697
Burning out now,
like a shooting star

00:06:05.073 --> 00:06:07.700
You can't kill my vibe, oh baby

00:06:07.784 --> 00:06:10.411
Burning out now,
like a shooting star

00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:18.753
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:06:34.769 --> 00:06:35.561
Huh?

00:06:35.561 --> 00:06:37.146
Stop!

00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:38.815
Stop right there!

00:06:38.898 --> 00:06:42.735
How dare you try to head into
the Royal Palace without waiting for me…

00:06:42.777 --> 00:06:45.196
…the great Ganju Shiba,

00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:47.782
the self-proclaimed expert
on the Royal Palace!

00:06:48.616 --> 00:06:50.493
Oh, it's you, Ganju…

00:06:50.535 --> 00:06:52.120
What are you doing here?

00:06:52.453 --> 00:06:53.621
That's a silly question!

00:06:53.704 --> 00:06:57.583
Who do you think launched
Squad Zero's Tenchuren?

00:06:57.583 --> 00:06:58.668
Your older sister.

00:06:58.793 --> 00:06:59.460
Exactly!

00:06:59.544 --> 00:07:00.545
It wasn't you.

00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:02.505
Right! It wasn't me!

00:07:02.505 --> 00:07:04.507
You don't give up, do you?

00:07:04.799 --> 00:07:06.717
So why are you here again?

00:07:06.801 --> 00:07:10.346
To go beat those Quincies,
of course!

00:07:10.721 --> 00:07:14.725
I even brought this roadmap to
the Royal Palace that I got from Sis!

00:07:14.809 --> 00:07:18.146
You can't get there without it!

00:07:18.229 --> 00:07:19.564
Are you sure about this?

00:07:20.106 --> 00:07:23.651
Ganju, the place we're headed to
is much more dangerous

00:07:23.734 --> 00:07:25.653
than any battle we've been in before.

00:07:26.112 --> 00:07:27.989
I know that, you idiot!

00:07:28.114 --> 00:07:30.283
That's why I'm going with you!

00:07:33.870 --> 00:07:34.996
Is that right?

00:07:36.914 --> 00:07:39.333
Okay, here goes.

00:07:52.722 --> 00:07:53.639
3…

00:07:54.682 --> 00:07:57.351
2…1…

00:08:00.188 --> 00:08:02.815
Oh, so this is how it flies?!

00:08:18.539 --> 00:08:21.209
That is one ugly lift-off.

00:08:21.542 --> 00:08:23.920
It couldn't have been adjusted
any worse.

00:08:25.963 --> 00:08:28.716
It's been a long time, Yhwach.

00:08:29.634 --> 00:08:33.513
Entering the Royal Palace uninvited.

00:08:33.721 --> 00:08:37.517
I can see defeating Genryusai
has really gotten to your head.

00:08:38.518 --> 00:08:39.519
Soldat!

00:08:40.561 --> 00:08:42.688
The Soul King's Blade.

00:08:53.074 --> 00:08:54.283
How discourteous.

00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:57.703
Become the rust on
the Soul King's Blade.

00:09:03.501 --> 00:09:06.462
You guys are way more discourteous.

00:09:06.671 --> 00:09:09.131
My Schrift is "W."

00:09:09.215 --> 00:09:12.301
Nianzol Weizol, "The Wind."

00:09:12.468 --> 00:09:14.053
Every enemy I find…

00:09:14.136 --> 00:09:18.516
bends and warps to avoid my body.

00:09:18.599 --> 00:09:20.309
STERN RITTER "W" – NIANZOL WEIZOL

00:09:20.601 --> 00:09:24.564
"Every enemy you find," you say?

00:09:24.939 --> 00:09:30.236
That means you cannot bend enemies
that cannot be detected.

00:09:30.987 --> 00:09:34.782
What I meant to say was that
I find my enemies through instinct.

00:09:35.449 --> 00:09:39.787
So, no matter where they attack from,
they steer clear of my body.

00:09:42.415 --> 00:09:44.834
Sorry for the lack of clarity.

00:09:45.084 --> 00:09:48.796
I get told all the time that
I have a bad habit

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:52.133
of not explaining things very well.

00:09:52.508 --> 00:09:54.635
Don't let it bother you.

00:09:54.677 --> 00:09:57.513
We all have our bad habits.

00:09:58.514 --> 00:10:01.517
An enemy is harder to see
the closer they are,

00:10:01.601 --> 00:10:05.229
especially if they're touching your body.

00:10:05.938 --> 00:10:08.649
Like the robe that you are wearing…

00:10:10.026 --> 00:10:13.279
While you were busy frolicking
with the Holy Soldiers,

00:10:14.447 --> 00:10:17.533
I retailored it with a fabric of my own.

00:10:18.576 --> 00:10:20.703
No way, this can't be…!

00:10:20.828 --> 00:10:23.873
The finest robe I sewed just for you.

00:10:23.998 --> 00:10:28.169
Be grateful that a foot soldier like you
even gets to wear it.

00:10:28.586 --> 00:10:29.670
And also…

00:10:30.004 --> 00:10:32.798
do not expect to take it off
before you die.

00:10:34.675 --> 00:10:35.885
Come to think of it,

00:10:35.968 --> 00:10:39.013
we were talking about our bad habits,
weren't we?

00:10:39.472 --> 00:10:44.727
Forgetting to remove my sewing needle
is a bad habit I can never break.

00:10:45.478 --> 00:10:47.021
This time, I'm the one

00:10:47.730 --> 00:10:51.525
who should apologize for
not explaining things clearly.

00:10:51.525 --> 00:10:52.985
"GREAT WEAVER" – SENJUMARU SHUTARA

00:10:55.988 --> 00:10:57.531
Gotta say…

00:10:57.531 --> 00:11:00.368
This turned into one hell of a mess.

00:11:00.534 --> 00:11:03.579
I thought for sure the Soul Reapers
were going to win.

00:11:04.038 --> 00:11:06.040
After building such a fine castle,

00:11:06.165 --> 00:11:08.042
I can't believe they'd just abandon it.

00:11:08.250 --> 00:11:11.712
Just what the hell is
this Yhwach guy thinking?

00:11:12.380 --> 00:11:15.132
So tell us, what exactly is
at the Royal Palace?

00:11:15.675 --> 00:11:19.053
Beats me. I've never been there myself.

00:11:19.136 --> 00:11:22.556
But I thought you said you were
the self-proclaimed expert

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:23.808
on the Royal Palace…

00:11:24.100 --> 00:11:27.561
Yeah, Sis told me all about it.

00:11:27.645 --> 00:11:29.689
I'm just not familiar with the small details.

00:11:29.730 --> 00:11:31.148
Is he serious?

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:36.362
They're going into the Royal Palace.

00:11:36.529 --> 00:11:38.906
That means their target is the Soul King.

00:11:39.281 --> 00:11:40.449
The Soul King…

00:11:41.117 --> 00:11:44.829
He is a god-like being that reigns
over all of the worlds:

00:11:44.912 --> 00:11:48.666
the Soul Society, the World of the Living,
and Hueco Mundo.

00:11:49.250 --> 00:11:51.335
I've only heard the stories of him, though.

00:11:51.419 --> 00:11:52.920
I've never met him.

00:11:53.337 --> 00:11:54.463
A god…

00:11:54.922 --> 00:11:57.967
Is that what Yhwach is trying to become?

00:11:58.175 --> 00:11:59.677
Yeah, that must be it!

00:12:01.721 --> 00:12:04.598
Is it even possible to replace
the Soul King?

00:12:05.391 --> 00:12:07.226
When I was training at
the Royal Palace,

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:09.895
I saw these images.

00:12:10.604 --> 00:12:14.608
The Soul King is supposed to be
the foundation of how the world works

00:12:14.692 --> 00:12:17.611
and an entity
that cannot be replaced.

00:12:17.695 --> 00:12:20.239
Then what is the enemy's objective?

00:12:20.322 --> 00:12:21.615
How should I know?!

00:12:22.158 --> 00:12:24.452
Well, we came this far.

00:12:24.577 --> 00:12:27.705
So whatever he's after,
we just have to kick their asses.

00:12:27.955 --> 00:12:29.123
You're right.

00:12:30.458 --> 00:12:33.085
This kind of brings back memories, huh?

00:12:33.627 --> 00:12:36.589
The time we went to go save Kuchiki…

00:12:37.339 --> 00:12:40.342
Back then, Yoruichi was still a cat and…

00:12:48.225 --> 00:12:50.102
…Ishida was with us, too.

00:12:57.651 --> 00:13:00.821
Do you think Ishida will
come back to us?

00:13:03.699 --> 00:13:04.992
Of course.

00:13:05.910 --> 00:13:08.496
We're on our way to take down Yhwach.

00:13:08.746 --> 00:13:11.540
And while we're at it,
we'll smack Ishida and drag him back!

00:13:11.707 --> 00:13:13.459
Isn't that what we decided?

00:13:14.502 --> 00:13:16.420
But that's secondary, of course.

00:13:18.339 --> 00:13:19.507
You're right!

00:13:22.718 --> 00:13:23.928
Well then…

00:13:24.220 --> 00:13:28.516
It seems our blades can finally
reach you.

00:13:29.266 --> 00:13:30.810
Do you really think so?

00:13:39.652 --> 00:13:41.695
My Royal Guards.

00:13:42.571 --> 00:13:44.698
We already know the answer.

00:13:44.865 --> 00:13:46.534
STERN RITTER "X" – LILLE BARRO

00:13:48.536 --> 00:13:50.371
STERN RITTER "C" – PERNIDA PARNKGJAS

00:13:50.704 --> 00:13:53.541
Whoa! Looks like I'm the only one
who had the privilege

00:13:53.666 --> 00:13:55.960
of being brought up from below.

00:13:56.252 --> 00:13:58.504
I'd better give a good showing…

00:13:59.129 --> 00:14:00.381
That's right!

00:14:00.589 --> 00:14:05.094
If you prove useless,
I will cut you down myself!

00:14:05.261 --> 00:14:06.887
STERN RITTER "M" – GERARD VALKYRIE

00:14:07.012 --> 00:14:09.640
I wouldn't want that after managing
to stay alive…

00:14:10.891 --> 00:14:15.062
A woman's slender arms
cannot stop my sword!

00:14:21.527 --> 00:14:24.196
Second Level Holy Soldier,
the Soul King's Shield!

00:14:24.363 --> 00:14:25.698
Stop them!

00:14:32.746 --> 00:14:34.623
Ah, you're pretty big!

00:14:36.584 --> 00:14:39.628
What? Is there something
you want to say?

00:14:39.753 --> 00:14:42.840
He said, "So what if he's big?"

00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:56.687
Are you finally starting to think
the Royal Palace might fall?

00:14:56.729 --> 00:14:58.355
It's too late.

00:14:58.522 --> 00:15:03.444
The losing side always realizes
and reacts too late.

00:15:03.944 --> 00:15:08.741
The Royal Palace fell the moment
His Majesty stepped foot here.

00:15:24.548 --> 00:15:28.594
ROYAL GUARDS

00:15:46.904 --> 00:15:48.614
Well, that was easy.

00:15:48.864 --> 00:15:50.658
Is that the best Squad Zero can do?

00:15:51.116 --> 00:15:53.953
Was there ever an opponent we faced…

00:15:54.036 --> 00:15:56.330
that wasn't easy?

00:16:01.877 --> 00:16:04.296
Everything in our way has fallen.

00:16:05.798 --> 00:16:07.591
After you, Your Majesty.

00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:15.516
What is this?

00:16:16.141 --> 00:16:17.685
The landscape of the Royal Palace is…

00:16:18.310 --> 00:16:19.687
What is going on?

00:16:20.020 --> 00:16:21.730
Where the hell are we?!

00:16:22.106 --> 00:16:27.695
This is a false Royal Palace built
to lure you in.

00:16:27.945 --> 00:16:33.575
The real Royal Palace is being
hidden over there by Osho.

00:16:34.827 --> 00:16:39.456
"HIDDEN"

00:16:39.707 --> 00:16:41.875
Ah! What's this?

00:16:41.959 --> 00:16:45.629
Did you gave it away already?
That must mean…

00:16:45.838 --> 00:16:48.257
the cage made it in time.

00:16:50.467 --> 00:16:51.427
What…?

00:16:51.927 --> 00:16:53.470
Yes, yes, yes, yes…

00:16:53.554 --> 00:16:55.472
I got it ready in time!

00:16:55.639 --> 00:16:59.560
It's been a while since I prepared
a womb this big.

00:16:59.768 --> 00:17:01.687
So it wasn't easy!

00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:05.858
Yikes… What is all this?

00:17:05.899 --> 00:17:08.068
Curse their bizarre tricks!

00:17:11.572 --> 00:17:13.907
It won't break even with
consecutive shots to the same spot.

00:17:14.533 --> 00:17:17.411
Even when I aim for the spaces,
the branches grow instantaneously.

00:17:18.537 --> 00:17:21.457
What a disgrace to
the "X-Axis" name, Lille!

00:17:21.540 --> 00:17:23.333
They did pierce it!

00:17:23.625 --> 00:17:28.005
Manipulating food
means manipulating life!

00:17:28.213 --> 00:17:31.258
I cook to shape lives.

00:17:31.425 --> 00:17:34.386
And the ingredients come from
my own body.

00:17:34.428 --> 00:17:38.057
This tree bears fruit by feeding on
my Spiritual Pressure.

00:17:38.557 --> 00:17:42.561
Your bullets are comprised of
highly concentrated Reishi, aren't they?

00:17:43.103 --> 00:17:47.524
This tree of life can't pass up
something that delicious.

00:17:47.816 --> 00:17:51.737
Even if they pierced through,
the tree grows at an even faster rate.

00:17:53.363 --> 00:17:55.449
You can struggle all you want.

00:17:55.532 --> 00:17:59.703
But your abilities can't escape
this Cage of Life.

00:18:01.622 --> 00:18:04.708
Don't be surprised just yet,
damn guests!

00:18:08.045 --> 00:18:10.756
Squad Zero First Officer,
Holy Guardian of the East,

00:18:10.881 --> 00:18:12.549
"Hot Spring Demon"!

00:18:12.633 --> 00:18:16.136
Tenjiro Kirinji! That's me!

00:18:16.261 --> 00:18:20.474
Squad Zero Fourth Officer,
Holy Guardian of the North…

00:18:20.599 --> 00:18:24.645
"Great Weaver." Senjumaru Shutara.

00:18:25.020 --> 00:18:28.607
Squad Zero Second Officer,
Holy Guardian of the South.

00:18:28.982 --> 00:18:32.319
"Grain King." Kirio Hikifune's the name.

00:18:35.656 --> 00:18:37.074
Yooo!

00:18:38.325 --> 00:18:42.162
I am the number one Zanpakuto creator!

00:18:42.621 --> 00:18:44.248
Ten, nine, eight, seven…

00:18:44.331 --> 00:18:45.499
six, five, four, three…

00:18:45.499 --> 00:18:49.128
Two, that's me, Oh-Etsu Nimaiya!

00:18:49.503 --> 00:18:52.339
There ain't no path for
you losers to walk on.

00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:56.385
Now shut up and
come at us altogether, yo.

00:18:56.635 --> 00:18:59.972
This is where Squad Zero's
real fight begins.

00:19:01.557 --> 00:19:02.516
Uh-oh…

00:19:02.641 --> 00:19:04.685
Maybe 'cause I haven't drawn this
in a long time…

00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:07.980
The blade feels wobbly!

00:19:10.065 --> 00:19:11.567
Nicely dodged!

00:19:11.692 --> 00:19:14.695
It's simple manners to dodge
a man's hug.

00:19:14.736 --> 00:19:15.779
Is that right?!

00:19:16.071 --> 00:19:17.614
Then the next attack…

00:19:19.449 --> 00:19:21.076
…is my turn.

00:19:23.579 --> 00:19:26.498
Huh? Wait…

00:19:26.498 --> 00:19:28.041
You're kidding me, right?

00:19:30.586 --> 00:19:33.463
Who do you think I am, yo?

00:19:33.463 --> 00:19:36.216
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six, five,

00:19:36.341 --> 00:19:37.801
four, three, two, that's me!

00:19:37.885 --> 00:19:43.724
Oh-Etsu Nimaiya.
The baddest man in Squad Zero.

00:19:44.725 --> 00:19:48.562
My sword kills with a single stroke, yo.

00:19:49.104 --> 00:19:50.856
You use a strange technique.

00:19:51.356 --> 00:19:53.400
Huh? Whatcha talkin' bout?

00:19:53.859 --> 00:19:56.486
It's a trick.
I can tell just from looking at it.

00:19:57.112 --> 00:19:59.990
That sword's been soaking in
that jelly-like substance.

00:20:00.407 --> 00:20:03.035
It's in such bad shape that
the blade wobbles.

00:20:03.493 --> 00:20:05.412
There's no way it can kill Gerard.

00:20:09.208 --> 00:20:10.751
What did you just do?

00:20:11.585 --> 00:20:12.628
Nothing.

00:20:13.420 --> 00:20:15.464
I simply held it like this,

00:20:15.547 --> 00:20:19.051
and your perfect bullseye shot
found its mark

00:20:19.134 --> 00:20:20.719
and was sliced right in two.

00:20:20.761 --> 00:20:22.137
That's all.

00:20:27.100 --> 00:20:27.768
What…?

00:20:41.615 --> 00:20:43.742
Oh! Nice move!

00:20:43.825 --> 00:20:47.120
You leapt backward in time matching
the speed of my blade.

00:20:47.162 --> 00:20:51.083
You couldn't have done that
without realizing how sharp this thing is.

00:20:51.708 --> 00:20:53.585
Guess you saw through it, eh?

00:20:57.297 --> 00:21:00.050
This "Sayafushi" is a failure.

00:21:00.133 --> 00:21:03.595
It's too sharp and
the blade is too smooth.

00:21:03.637 --> 00:21:06.265
The edge never chips
no matter how much I cut with it.

00:21:06.473 --> 00:21:09.601
It's gonna put us swordsmiths
out of work.

00:21:09.893 --> 00:21:13.939
And most importantly,
I can't create a sheath that can hold it.

00:21:14.273 --> 00:21:17.484
Since it's not a complete sword,

00:21:17.526 --> 00:21:20.654
I couldn't send it down
to the Seireitei.

00:21:21.321 --> 00:21:24.408
I'm glad you guys stormed
the Royal Palace.

00:21:24.491 --> 00:21:26.910
Thanks to you,
I got a chance to put this to use.

00:21:27.661 --> 00:21:30.956
I appreciate it, Y.H.!

00:21:48.181 --> 00:21:50.809
So, you have the power to escape
from the womb?

00:21:50.851 --> 00:21:52.978
I'm impressed.

00:21:53.395 --> 00:21:56.523
Gotta hand it to the King.
A brilliant rising!

00:21:57.357 --> 00:21:59.526
Aren't you going to go
after His Majesty?

00:21:59.693 --> 00:22:02.195
I should be asking you guys
the same question!

00:22:02.404 --> 00:22:03.447
Up above is Osho.

00:22:03.530 --> 00:22:08.493
Even my hot springs can't wash away
his bloody stench.

00:22:08.785 --> 00:22:12.706
He sure likes to say all sorts of things
about me when I'm not around.

00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:15.000
What are your thoughts on that?

00:22:16.460 --> 00:22:20.589
You will let me through,
Ichibe Hyosube.

00:22:22.674 --> 00:22:27.220
I've chastised you many times,
and yet you still say my name lightly.

00:22:29.097 --> 00:22:31.892
Don't blame me
if you lose your voice.

00:22:31.892 --> 00:22:34.436
"MANAKO OSHO" – ICHIBE HYOSUBE

00:22:44.571 --> 00:22:48.909
All at once, the lights went out

00:22:48.950 --> 00:22:50.160
Reminding me

00:22:50.243 --> 00:22:51.411
with a voice

00:22:51.495 --> 00:22:53.663
and I cannot move

00:22:54.414 --> 00:22:58.585
Unable to convey even a millimeter

00:22:58.668 --> 00:22:59.795
of the lines that I dubbed

00:22:59.878 --> 00:23:03.507
All lines
that I don't want to forget

00:23:03.507 --> 00:23:04.758
Rewound

00:23:04.883 --> 00:23:05.926
Repeated

00:23:06.009 --> 00:23:07.094
Became a mark

00:23:07.177 --> 00:23:08.428
And I notice the dust

00:23:08.428 --> 00:23:09.513
I wait and wait

00:23:09.596 --> 00:23:11.014
But it won't start

00:23:11.098 --> 00:23:12.099
If it's already ended

00:23:12.182 --> 00:23:13.517
I give up

00:23:13.558 --> 00:23:14.559
But can I

00:23:14.601 --> 00:23:15.769
borrow your shoulder?

00:23:15.894 --> 00:23:17.479
With that knife

00:23:17.479 --> 00:23:19.648
that was left behind

00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:22.442
Pierce it through

00:23:22.526 --> 00:23:23.777
Still

00:23:23.819 --> 00:23:26.113
in the middle of a dream,

00:23:26.154 --> 00:23:28.615
We kept searching

00:23:28.657 --> 00:23:30.784
For the scar that

00:23:30.867 --> 00:23:33.495
the revolving world remembers

00:23:33.578 --> 00:23:35.747
With just the strong desire

00:23:35.831 --> 00:23:39.126
to keep on living

00:23:39.209 --> 00:23:44.297
We'll choose a tomorrow
that will not return

00:23:44.381 --> 00:23:48.969
In just a little while

00:23:49.094 --> 00:23:53.598
The final curtain will fall

00:23:54.224 --> 00:23:57.769
Shining upon us

00:23:57.811 --> 00:24:00.647
The blurred end roll

00:24:14.578 --> 00:24:19.082
"The future, pitch black, upside down."

